name: MeanFortune
0:
”Alexa open mean fortune”
”Alexa ask mean fortune for a fortune”
”Alexa tell mean fortune to give me a fortune”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mean fortune
des: Ask for your fortune, if you dare. Mean Fortune delivers humorous and insulting fortunes. The cookie knows what your future holds. To start, just say "Alexa, launch Mean Fortune" or "Alexa, open Mean Fortune" to get a fortune". At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
